{"word":"G2974 - κωφός - kōphós - ko-fos' - Deaf","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κωφός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kōphós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ko-fos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Deaf</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஊமையான, செவிடான, பேசக்கூடாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"blunted, dull"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2875 - κόπτω - kóptō - kop'-to/2875\">G2875</a>; <i>blunted</i>, that is, (figuratively) of hearing (<i>deaf</i>) or speech (<i>dumb</i>): - deaf, dumb, speechless.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}